Global Risks Growing, Markets Volatile, S. Korea’s Bahk Says

-- B y   E u n k y u n g   S e o
-- 
2011-09-15T23:22:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/global-risks-growing-markets-volatile-s-korea-s-bahk-says.html
Global economic risks are growing
and financial markets are highly volatile,  South Korea ’s Finance
Minister Bahk Jae Wan said. Some food prices have stabilized in
recent weeks on increased production, Bahk said at a ministerial
meeting today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
